descriptionHtml:
Did you go to a private doctor’s clinic several times and did not find him for any reason? Did you wait your turn in the doctor clinic for a long time?? All this has become in the past, through the application of your Hajzak Altebi
* Hajzak Altebi application contains a database includes all medical specialties (more than 50 different medical specialties) including internal doctors, pediatricians, ophthalmologists, cardiologists, urologists, dentists, and others ... It also includes the help agencies for doctors in their work like medical laboratories, medical imaging units, physiotherapy units and other medical services.

* By using Hajzak Altebi application You can apply to search for doctor who you want through three different ways: the location of doctor's clinic using Google Map, search by the required specialization, and search by the name of the doctor.

* By using Hajzak Altebi application You can estimate doctor’s medical services that you visited and you can see the doctor’s evaluation from other patients.

* Through Hajzak Altebi application You can reserve the medical information about the doctor you want to book with, such as his specialty, place of study and the university from which he graduated, current work place, previous work place, the scout price, the doctor active times in the clinic, and the time period between each patient.

* The application of Hajzak Altebi reminds the patient of his doctor's appointment before 24 hours from the appointment which he has chosen.

* Through Hajzak Altebi application You can write any problem you may encounter in booking your appointments.

* Hajzak Altebi application helping to submit an apology for attending the clinic by the doctor. In addition, the patient can submit his apology to the doctor and you can write the apology reasons.

* Hajzak Altebi application helping to contact directly with doctors' numbers through WhatsApp, or direct contact with them on their own phones.

* The application enables you to track your appointments that you have reserved for doctors by providing the date, time and day for your appointments.

* The application of Hajzak Altebi applies the events of the patient's medical file as a kind of archiving to the patient, and the doctor concerned can see that file by requesting the patient's identification number, instead of carrying the previous medical reports, also the doctor can amend this medical file if he wants.

* Hajzak Altebi application modify to change doctors working hours anywhere and anytime, also the doctor works on adding several clinics on the same account if he works in several different clinics.

* Hajzak Altebi application enables the patient to access all of your upcoming completed and canceled reservations made through the application.

* Hajzak Altebi application is a leading application to book your medical appointments with the doctor you want, all you have to download the application from the store for easy processing so that you can get all the medical services related to booking appointments with doctors.
